edu.memphis.ccrg.lida.framework.gui.utils
Class GuiLink

java.lang.Object
  edu.memphis.ccrg.lida.framework.gui.utils.GuiLink

public class GuiLink
extends java.lang.Object

Utility which NodeStructurePanel uses to represent Links. This represents a Link in the Panel. For every Link we create two GuiLinks: The first GuiLink has type 'S' for "source". It connects the source of the Link to the Link itself. The second GuiLink has type 'D' for "destination". It connects the Link itself to the sink of the Link

Author:
Javier Snaider
